race.comment: MEAT PIE ARTIE (4) led and bolted in over this course and distance last start, running away to score by 2.4L. He draws a little better today and can take up the running once more. Drops in weight today and rates highly on his latest effort. Can repeat the dose. ZADOWS LANDING (3) made it three in-a-row last start over the mile at this course and comes back in trip today. The niggle is him coming back to 1300m today, but the gun for hire Wheatley is on board. Can continue his strong run of recent form. LACIE ACE (11) is better than she showed last start when stepping up to the mile and never getting into the race. She's more effective at this trip, having won over 1400m two starts back. Maps nicely along the inside and a sharp turnaround in form is on the cards. MORE LIKELY (5) has the figures to feature and is not to be discounted. SECRICITY (6) is not out of this if she can run up to recent form.
